WEBVTT

00:00.200 --> 00:02.833
Are you taking part in the singing contest next week?

00:03.185 --> 00:04.497
Yes. You too?

00:05.109 --> 00:07.599
Please feel at home, and help yourself to some beer.

00:08.292 --> 00:10.100
Sure, I will. Thank you.

00:11.027 --> 00:15.086
I am a bit nervous now because I need to make a speech in public tomorrow.

00:16.175 --> 00:20.026
Liz failed the exam in spite of all her efforts the day before.

00:21.272 --> 00:22.399
She was very sad.

00:23.685 --> 00:25.740
I am a member of the basketball club.

